OL,3,CAer Lingus to cancel up to 20% of
OL,4,Cflights amid pilots' action
OL,6,FAer Lingus passengers who are impacted
OL,7,Fby pilots' industrial action next week
OL,8,Fare to be contacted by the airline
OL,9,Ffrom Friday.
OL,11,FPilots at Aer Lingus are to begin an
OL,12,Findefinite work-to-rule from next
OL,13,FWednesday after balloting for
OL,14,Findustrial action, which means they
OL,15,Fwill not engage in overtime or out-of-
OL,16,Fhours duties.
OL,18,FThe move has been branded as
OL,19,F"insidious" by the company, which is
OL,20,Fcancelling up to 20% of flights over a
OL,21,Ffive-day period.
