OL,3,CAer Lingus to cancel up to 20% of
OL,4,Cflights amid pilots' action
OL,6,FDonal Moriarty, chief corporate
OL,7,Faffairs officer with Aer Lingus, said
OL,8,Fthey were taking the move to prevent
OL,9,Ffurther cancellations.
OL,11,FHe said that this form of industrial
OL,12,Faction "gets worse day by day" and
OL,13,Fthat there was a risk that further
OL,14,Fcancellations would be needed.
