OL,3,CAer Lingus to cancel up to 20% of
OL,4,Cflights amid pilots' action
OL,6,F"What will happen over the next couple
OL,7,Fof days is that impacted passengers
OL,8,Fwill be contacted and advised of
OL,9,Fcancellations if it affects them and
OL,10,Fthen given their options in terms of
OL,11,Frefund, re-accommodation or voucher,"
OL,12,Fhe told RTE Radio.
OL,14,FHe said that people have also been
OL,15,Fgiven the option to cancel or rebook
OL,16,Ftheir flights for a later date for
OL,17,Ffree.
