OL,3,CAer Lingus to cancel up to 20% of
OL,4,Cflights amid pilots' action
OL,6,FPilots, represented by the Irish
OL,7,FAirline Pilots' Association (Ialpa),
OL,8,Fare seeking a pay increase of 24%,
OL,9,Fwhich they say equates to inflation
OL,10,Fsince the last pay rise in 2019.
OL,12,FAer Lingus has described the pay
OL,13,Fdemand as unrealistic and said there
OL,14,Fhad been no pay deals in Ireland that
OL,15,Fdelivered such an increase.
