OL,3,CAer Lingus to cancel up to 20% of
OL,4,Cflights amid pilots' action
OL,6,FIrish premier Simon Harris said it was
OL,7,F"utterly reprehensible" that children
OL,8,Fdue to go on holiday were being "used
OL,9,Fas pawns" in the industrial relations
OL,10,Fdispute and urged the airline and the
OL,11,Fpilots to "sort this out".
OL,13,FMr Moriarty said: "We would like to
OL,14,Fengage in direct discussions with
OL,15,FIalpa to reach a reasonable settlement
OL,16,Fto this pay dispute and we are trying
OL,17,Fto do that but unfortunately Ialpa
OL,18,Fended those discussions last Monday."
