OL,6,FHe said that Aer Lingus pilots are
OL,7,Falready paid "very well" and said
OL,8,Ftheir salaries were "in line" with the
OL,9,Fmarket rates.
OL,11,F"There is a pay deal on offer to them
OL,12,Fof 12.25% increase, which they've
OL,13,Fdeclined," he said.
OL,15,F"We have also tried to discuss with
OL,16,Fthem building upon that over and above
OL,17,F12.25% by discussing improvements in
OL,18,Fproductivity and flexibility, but
OL,19,Funfortunately Ialpa have been
OL,20,Funwilling (to engage) with those
OL,21,Fdiscussions."
